I don’t know where you are, but I love you today and always. Please come home when you’re
ready darling. I’ll be here.
His owl had flown off with the package and returned several hours later empty-handed, so he
knew she received it. There was nothing more that he could do.
His thoughts were interrupted by Patsy, who appeared with a CRACK!
“Pardon me, Master, but this note was just delivered for you.”
Draco furrowed his brow and accepted it. Then his stomach dropped when he recognized
