Draco looked at her in confusion. “Okay?” he said. He had no idea what was going on.
“Are you ready to be a father?”
Draco gave a mirthless laugh. “Of course not. Is anybody ever ready the first time?”
Hermione narrowed her eyes. “But you still want to be?”
Draco frowned. “I don’t want to sway any decision or –”
