about a marriage law, eh? And my granddaughter went to prison? Well she wouldn’t be the
first one in the family, though it’s been a few generations. I think the last time it happened
was over some gambling debts. Or perhaps a duel at sunrise to defend a lady’s honor, and the
idiots involved got caught. The family history has never been entirely clear on this point.”
