Watching Isabella Granger was like looking fifty years into the future. She was obviously
very fond of Hermione, though it had been quite some time since they had caught up. Based
on a few nuggets she dropped, however, Draco sensed that Hermione may have seen her gran
on occasion, even when the relationship with her parents was very strained. She was funny
