He pulled back and studied her curiously. “A babymoon?”
“Yes, it’s something muggles do on occasion. It’s a sort of last hurrah trip for the parents
before the baby is born. We never took a honeymoon, you know, and everyone says to take
the babymoon during the second trimester. I thought this could be a good time to do it before
I’m busy with exams for the students and you’re busy with the MLPP repeal.”
Draco relaxed into a smile. “You’re right we didn’t take a honeymoon, did we? I’ll need to
reschedule some meetings next week, but I’m sure I can be free for a babymoon. Do you
