“Maybe the Amalfi coast? I’ve always wanted to see it.”
“That’s one of the easiest places you could have picked,” said Draco, with a smile. “Just tell
me the days you want to be there, and I’ll plan everything. Blaise actually has a villa in
Positano if that’s acceptable? It’s been years since I’ve visited, but I’m sure he would let us
use it. He only goes there in the winter.”
Hermione beamed, and Draco felt a leap of pleasure at this. She wanted to vacation with
him. She wanted to take a trip like a normal couple about to become parents. Surely, surely
