“Oh dear, he doesn’t like being disturbed, does he?” asked Helen in amusement.
Draco found his nerves easing, and he chuckled a bit.
“Stubborn little thing…” commented the muggle. “Come on, baby… let us see…”
“He takes after his mother,” said David, and Draco heard Hermione huff in irritation as the
