“The doctor will talk to you about it. I’m just a technician.”
Draco’s stomach inexplicably knotted.
“But–” started Hermione.
“Nothing to worry about,” said the muggle. “I’m just making notes of measurements, that’s
all. Now then, would you like to hear his heartbeat?”
This had the effect of diverting the grandparents, but Hermione and Draco exchanged slightly
