Draco exchanged a concerned look with Hermione.
“You don’t think he’s a threat, do you?” she asked.
Potter shook his head. “No, not really. I gave him a pretty stern warning after the vote of no
confidence. But he’s not pleased, and he is a former auror. He wasn’t invited tonight, you
