Draco’s mouth thinned at this, but he nodded at Potter. “Please keep an eye on it.”
“Of course I will,” he said, exchanging a knowing look with Draco. “Hermione is my best
friend, and other than my wife and child she’s my top priority. And Kingsley will get over it,
