Draco had been unfortunately reminded of him after Hermione’s appointment the previous
day, in which his photographic dildo evidently made its first appearance.
The dildo may be his, but the baby is mine, Draco told himself.
Still, he made a point to turn Hermione and kiss her directly in front of Rita Skeeter just to
